，许多纳粹主义意识形态再次试图向世界兜售。那些实施侵略计划、反犹太主义和仇俄情绪的人不容宽恕和辩解。 普京称，那些忘记二战教训、再次酝酿侵略计划的人是不可原谅的。「战争带来了许多难以忍受的苦难、悲伤和眼泪，这一点是不能忘记的。」 普京说称苏联人民对纳粹主义做出历史性判决。「苏联人民履行了这一神圣的誓言，捍卫了自己的祖国，使欧洲国家摆脱了法西斯，对纳粹主义做出历史性判决。」 普京说：「历史要求得出结论并汲取经验。但不幸的是，还有试图再次武装纳粹意识形态的许多东西以及那些痴迷于排他性妄想理论的人，不仅各种激进分子或国际恐怖分子团伙。」 普京称，俄罗斯始终不渝地捍卫国际法，同时将坚定捍卫国家利益，确保俄罗斯人民的安全。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-76fbd86c0f854a87265fe19c4bba3427_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "74 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/458555627"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI8cfM5ZHcuo8kEAMaCDY0MTgxNTY5IOX73oQGMAI4vgFAJHIJNDU4NTU1NjI3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "37_1620626795.9001389", "card_id": "Q_458178634", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 36}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何知道一个猫咪喜欢吃什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-03d7b6690a90ea0d248d54a60a93b370_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "73 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/458178634"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I8cfM5ZHcuo8kEAMaCDY0MDk3NzE3IILl0oQGMAA4LUAlcgk0NTgxNzg2MzR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1620626795.9005976", "card_id": "Q_394874619", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 9260}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "一个很爱你的人真的可以忍住很长时间都不联系你吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-e16b3da70d4278985784885cd6dbcada_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "72 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/394874619"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8cfM5ZHcuo8kEAMaCDUwMDI5MDEwIPKy9fUFMBY4+lFAJnIJMzk0ODc0NjE5eACq